  "text": "Response Criteria. Each patient's total tumor load was established by summing bidimensional tumor measurements that were obtained from CT scan, in which the longest diameter of each lesion was multiplied by its perpendicular diameter. Response to treatment was classified in accordance with modified WHO criteria [CITATION_1] .",
